name: Tipinu
description: The Tipinu token is the second token released as part of the Cummuniti and Cuminu token ecosystem. The Butter token has auto-liquidity, deflationary, and staking reward mechanics. The Tipinu Token is used as the tipping utility token on the Cummuniti platform. Tipinu token automatically collects 10% fees on every transaction that are used to buy-back Cuminu and permanently remove them from circulation.
